title_synonyms: My Girlfriend is a Faithful Virgin Bitch
Boku no Kanojo ga Majimesugiru Shojo Bitch na Ken
data.synopsis:
Haruka Shinozaki has been interested in the class representative, Akiho Kousaka, since his first year in high school. She is attractive, good at sports, and is an all-around model student. Since they are in the same class this year, Shinozaki decides to confess his feelings—and, to his shock, Kousaka agrees to be his girlfriend!

However, he finds that Kousaka is a bit stranger than he first thought: this seemingly perfect girl has never been in a relationship. But even though she is inexperienced, she vows to please Shinozaki in every way she can... such as learning multiple sex positions or his fetishes. Shinozaki tries to assure her that her studies into such subjects aren't necessary, but Kousaka devotes herself to making him happy in more ways than one.

[Written by MAL Rewrite]

titles.title: Yamishibai: Japanese Ghost Stories Fifth Season
Yamishibai: Historias Japonesas de Fantasmas Temporada 5

data.title: Yami Shibai 5
title_synonyms: Yamishibai: Japanese Ghost Stories Fifth Season
data.synopsis:
The mysterious masked Storyteller returns to tell more twisted tales of horror. Continuing his particular style of kamishibai inspired storytelling, he now finds that his audience is an eerie crowd of young girls, who eagerly await his devilish stories.

He recounts ghostly legends involving girls of all ages: a housewife who receives a barrage of chilling phone calls; a strange girl whose flower readings are always right; a mother and daughter's ominous meeting with the "crow lady"; and a young girl whose demands from others grow more and more outrageous with each request. Witness once again the Storyteller's haunting and gripping tales, which are sure to leave one with more than just chills...

[Written by MAL Rewrite]

data.title: ACCA: 13-ku Kansatsu-ka Specials
data.synopsis:
The Kingdom of Dowa is free at last of political tensions and coup d'état rumors. Jean and Lotta Otus spend their days together with their best friend Niino, enjoying carefree conversations accompanied by alcohol and cigarettes. Although they look out for any potential threat to Dowa, even the administrative leaders of ACCA seem to relax in the long-awaited warmth of peace.

[Written by MAL Rewrite]
